    "name": "Mandila Beach Hotel DaNang",
    "detail": "When evrything went oke a very nice place to stay for a combination trip to Da nang. The country gave me much inspiration, I started in Hoi An, visit the old town, meet very kind people, how helped me a lot. It was more personally than in Da Nang., but good for me, because I want to write a book,. Someday My money was gone in my room. I think I know why that happened and was my ouwn fault I believe. I booked the hotel two times, because I decided to go earlier to DA Nang. More time for writing. I kept the same room. Evry day I looked how much money I took with me when I went out for a drink, or eat. I sleept my time over the first morning of the second period, I had an appointment for cleaning face and hair and leave in a hurry. It must be certain, I left my other money on the desk because of that. 200 Euro, 50 American Dollar and Hong Kong dollars ( small amount ). Someone must have decided that it was my tip. Well you can,t say nothing. The manager helped me try to find out, 👍👍👍",
